title: [Fist Class Plane Ticket]
description: Oddly uncluttered and free of dust considering the rather near-haphazard construction of the shop, darkly stained wood attempts to hide some of the aging and flaws.  In contrast, two new-looking containers are bedecked with various wares organized in pristine arrangement.  Panels of indigo velvet drape from the ceiling centerpoint out to the walls in the four cardinal directions, each emblazoned with vaalin stars and opal moons.
